Class MapController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301fa16t5.legendary_telegram.MapController

  • public class MapController
extends java.lang.Object
    MapController class is the controller of the map. It is used to create the URL according to different parameters. It is also used to sent the URL to the server and get JSON object return.
